      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense, but u said it \"inevitably leads to conflict.\" isn't that a bit of an exaggeration? like, surely a country can have a strong national identity without being aggressive or erasing minorities. u seem to be implying that the \"danger\" part is basically baked into the idea itself.",
